gate: LOCKED
sprint: S04
track: C
task: C6
title: "chore(deps): knip dead-code cleanup + make dead:check blocking (#1391)"
repos: [crop-front]
priority: P3
refs:
  - CROP-front#1391
requires: [TYPESCRIPT]

description: |
  knip identifies dead exports and unused files but the check is currently
  non-blocking in CI. Fix in two steps:
  1. Delete all dead code identified by knip (run `bunx knip`, remove findings).
  2. Flip dead:check to blocking so future dead code additions fail CI.

scope:
  in:
    - Run `bunx knip` — capture full list of dead exports/files
    - Delete dead code (exports, files, types flagged by knip)
    - Verify `bunx knip` returns 0 findings after cleanup
    - Flip CI gate to blocking (package.json script or workflow step)
  out:
    - Changing any live code behaviour
    - Fixing ESLint or TypeScript errors unrelated to dead code

acceptance:
  - `bunx knip` exits 0 after cleanup
  - CI dead:check gate is blocking
  - No runtime regressions (typecheck + tests green)

dep: none
output: deleted dead files/exports + CI gate update
